<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 08:10:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>乌克兰无人机在俄罗斯别尔哥罗德地区击落一人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukrainian-drone-kills-one-in-russias-belgorod-region/articleshow/110295340.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110295340.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;别尔哥罗德俄罗斯边境地区州长周二表示，乌克兰无人机袭击导致一名妇女死亡，另有三人受伤。别尔哥罗德州州长维亚切斯拉夫·格拉德科夫（Vyacheslav Gladkov）在 Telegram 上发帖称：“一架神风特攻队无人机袭击了一辆行驶中的汽车，车上有一名司机和三名乘客。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 07:19:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukrainian-drone-kills-one-in-russias-belgorod-region/articleshow/110295340.cms</guid></item><item><title>牧场的消亡“被严重低估”：《联合国防治荒漠化公约》报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/demise-of-rangelands-severely-underestimated-unccd-report/articleshow/110294746.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110294746.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;研究人员警告说，世界上多达一半的牧场已经退化，对传统牧民产生了影响。气候变化和土地转化加剧了破坏，影响了全球变暖和生物多样性热点。 《联合国防治荒漠化公约》强调土壤健康对于储存碳的重要性。牧场支持非洲标志性的野生动物、国民经济和文化遗产。它们对于粮食生产、牧民社区和保护多样化语言至关重要。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 07:06:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/demise-of-rangelands-severely-underestimated-unccd-report/articleshow/110294746.cms</guid></item><item><title>九名埃及人被控在希腊造成致命移民沉船事故，审判开始</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/trial-begins-for-nine-egyptians-accused-in-deadly-migrant-shipwreck-in-greece/articleshow/110294356.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110294356.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;九名埃及男子因造成海难导致数百名移民死亡而在希腊南部面临审判。被告大多年龄在 20 多岁，如果因“阿德里安娜”号拖网渔船沉没的多项刑事指控被定罪，他们可能面临终身监禁。此次审判引发了人们对边境保护和庇护行动的担忧，目前对希腊海岸警卫队救援行动的调查仍在进行中。国际人权组织认为，被告获得公平审判的权利可能会受到损害。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 06:57:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/trial-begins-for-nine-egyptians-accused-in-deadly-migrant-shipwreck-in-greece/articleshow/110294356.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队袭击约旦河西岸杰宁，巴勒斯坦人称七人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-army-raids-west-banks-jenin-palestinians-say-seven-killed/articleshow/110293820.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110293820.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列军队袭击了西岸的杰宁，杀死了医院附近的七名巴勒斯坦人，其中包括一名担任杰宁政府医院院长的外科医生。在针对巴勒斯坦武装分子的行动中另有九人受伤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 06:40:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-army-raids-west-banks-jenin-palestinians-say-seven-killed/articleshow/110293820.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国开始对叙利亚官员进行首次战争罪审判</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/france-begins-its-first-war-crime-trial-of-syrian-officials/articleshow/110292183.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110292183.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法国对叙利亚巴沙尔·阿萨德政权官员的首次审判将于周二开始，三名高级安全官员将因共犯危害人类罪和战争罪而接受缺席审判。代表达巴格家族和国际人权联合会的律师克莱门斯·贝克塔特表示，这次审判再次提醒人们，“在任何情况下”都不应与阿萨德政权实现关系正常化。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 05:54:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/france-begins-its-first-war-crime-trial-of-syrian-officials/articleshow/110292183.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：反对派联盟向法院寻求集会许可</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-opposition-alliance-approaches-court-to-seek-permission-for-rally/articleshow/110291845.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110291845.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦反对派联盟寻求允许在伊斯兰堡举行公众集会，以“恢复”宪法。该运动涉及各种政治人物，并包括在卡拉奇和费萨拉巴德举行权力表演的计划。 PTI 请求法院命令当局不要对参加公开集会的任何人使用武力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 05:46:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-opposition-alliance-approaches-court-to-seek-permission-for-rally/articleshow/110291845.cms</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥热浪：几只吼猴死亡，当局正在进行调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mexico-heatwave-several-howler-monkeys-drop-dead-authorities-investigate/articleshow/110292275.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110292275.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 06:05:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mexico-heatwave-several-howler-monkeys-drop-dead-authorities-investigate/articleshow/110292275.cms</guid></item><item><title>厄瓜多尔消防队员向五只退役救援犬授予荣誉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ecuadors-firefighters-bestow-honors-on-five-retired-rescue-dogs/articleshow/110288779.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110288779.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;五只救援犬：阿瑞斯、奎托斯、宙斯、泰坦和盖亚，在厄瓜多尔消防队服役 7 年后退役。埃斯特班·卡德纳斯 (Esteban Cardenas) 中校赞扬了他们在厄瓜多尔和国外的地震和山体滑坡救援中所发挥的作用，包括 2017 年前往墨西哥与德国牧羊犬和金毛猎犬一起执行任务。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ecuadors-firefighters-bestow-honors-on-five-retired-rescue-dogs/articleshow/110288779.cms</guid></item><item><title>世界领导人将在首尔峰会上通过新的人工智能协议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/world-leaders-to-adopt-new-ai-agreement-at-seoul-summit/articleshow/110291638.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110291638.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;包括韩国总统尹锡烈和英国首相里希·苏纳克在内的世界领导人将虚拟聚集在首尔人工智能峰会上，通过一项关于人工智能的新协议，并与 Meta、OpenAI、谷歌等行业领导者一起讨论其潜在风险和收益、Facebook 和 Amazon，最近加入了前沿模型论坛。法国承诺举办一次成熟的现场峰会，开发人员正在通过 Anthropic 创立的前沿模型论坛制定共享的人工智能安全标准。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 05:37:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/world-leaders-to-adopt-new-ai-agreement-at-seoul-summit/articleshow/110291638.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国和菲律宾将培训菲律宾人进行核电培训</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-philippines-to-train-filipinos-in-nuclear-power/articleshow/110291657.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110291657.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;根据马尼拉和华盛顿之间的协议，菲律宾和美国同意培训菲律宾人建设和运营核电站。丹尼尔·克里滕布林克和菲律宾能源部将提供奖学金和交换项目。菲律宾能源部长拉斐尔·洛蒂拉强调了该国人力资源“高级培训”的重要性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 05:38:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-philippines-to-train-filipinos-in-nuclear-power/articleshow/110291657.cms</guid></item><item><title>人民币汇率触及三个月低点后触及三周以来最低水平</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/chinas-yuan-hits-weakest-level-in-3-weeks-after-fix-set-at-3-month-low/articleshow/110289396.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110289396.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于央行下调指导利率以打击资本外流，人民币兑美元走弱。周二，人民币兑美元汇率跌至三周低点。马银行分析师将人民币贬值与资本外流恶化以及对住房救助计划资金的担忧联系起来。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:23:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/chinas-yuan-hits-weakest-level-in-3-weeks-after-fix-set-at-3-month-low/articleshow/110289396.cms</guid></item><item><title>重要会议召开，巴黎争夺欧洲人工智能桂冠</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/paris-vies-for-europes-ai-crown-as-key-conference-beckons/articleshow/110290735.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110290735.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法国在 Viva Technology 举办技术领袖峰会，希望巩固巴黎作为人工智能中心的地位。 LVMH 旗下的 Arnault 展示奢侈品牌。马克龙利用巴黎的奢华地位吸引了对生成型人工智能初创公司的投资。亚马逊和微软在法国科技领域进行投资，努力整合资本市场并吸引科技投资。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 05:09:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/paris-vies-for-europes-ai-crown-as-key-conference-beckons/articleshow/110290735.cms</guid></item><item><title>新加坡在马来西亚警察局袭击后加强安全</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/singapore-boosts-security-after-malaysia-police-station-attack/articleshow/110291242.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110291242.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新加坡总理黄循财周二表示，一名涉嫌与基地组织有联系的男子袭击了邻国马来西亚的一个警察局，新加坡加强了安全措施。新加坡新当选总理黄说：“这样的袭击发生在我们的边界之外，无情地提醒我们恐怖主义的威胁仍然很高。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 05:25:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/singapore-boosts-security-after-malaysia-police-station-attack/articleshow/110291242.cms</guid></item><item><title>周二的初选包括总统竞选和特朗普佐治亚州选举案中的检察官</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/tuesdays-primaries-include-presidential-races-and-the-prosecutor-in-trumps-georgia-election-case/articleshow/110290234.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110290234.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乔·拜登和唐纳德·特朗普的总统初选即将结束，随着肯塔基州和俄勒冈州即将做出的象征性决定，他们面临着异议。影响全国代表大会、代表，并揭示民主党和共和党基础的情绪。各种州初选和关键竞选在多个州展开，包括佐治亚州、加利福尼亚州和俄勒冈州，在区和县级别都有重要的比赛。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:50:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/tuesdays-primaries-include-presidential-races-and-the-prosecutor-in-trumps-georgia-election-case/articleshow/110290234.cms</guid></item><item><title>所罗门群岛告诉澳大利亚它仍然是首选合作伙伴</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/solomon-islands-tells-australia-it-remains-partner-of-choice/articleshow/110289947.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110289947.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新当选的所罗门群岛总理马内莱寻求扩大与澳大利亚的合作，以应对中国在该地区的影响。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:41:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/solomon-islands-tells-australia-it-remains-partner-of-choice/articleshow/110289947.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国因用受污染的血液感染数千人并掩盖丑闻而受到调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britain-slammed-in-inquiry-for-infecting-thousands-with-tainted-blood-and-covering-up-the-scandal/articleshow/110288861.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110288861.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一项调查揭露英国当局通过受污染的血液使患者遭受致命感染，导致死亡和终身疾病。前法官布赖恩·兰斯塔夫批评了国家医疗服务体系，并强调了艾滋病毒感染的影响。报告还提到使用高危捐献者的血浆以及通过输血传播丙型肝炎。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:02:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britain-slammed-in-inquiry-for-infecting-thousands-with-tainted-blood-and-covering-up-the-scandal/articleshow/110288861.cms</guid></item><item><title>澳元、新西兰元已经耗尽，思考利率前景</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/australia-nz-dollars-run-out-of-puff-ponder-rate-outlooks/articleshow/110288780.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110288780.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于市场评估利率稳定，澳元和新西兰元走弱。铜价飙升至历史新高，支撑主要大宗商品。澳洲联储发布会议纪要，暗示可能加息，等待通胀和消费者数据。新西兰联储预计将维持官方现金利率不变，市场预计八月份可能会降息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/australia-nz-dollars-run-out-of-puff-ponder-rate-outlooks/articleshow/110288780.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列和哈马斯拒绝国际刑事法院以战争罪逮捕领导人的请求</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-reject-bid-before-icc-to-arrest-leaders-for-war-crimes/articleshow/110288757.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110288757.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列和哈马斯在美国的反对下拒绝了国际刑事法院检察官卡里姆·汗在加沙地带逮捕战争罪领导人的请求，南非对国际刑事法院的举动表示欢迎，而法国则表示支持法院的独立性“以及反对恐怖主义的斗争”。在所有情况下都不受惩罚&amp;quot;。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 03:58:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-reject-bid-before-icc-to-arrest-leaders-for-war-crimes/articleshow/110288757.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在真相社交视频中发表“统一帝国”的帖子引发愤怒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-sparks-outrage-with-unified-reich-post-in-truth-social-video/articleshow/110288852.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110288852.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:02:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-sparks-outrage-with-unified-reich-post-in-truth-social-video/articleshow/110288852.cms</guid></item><item><title>谷物-小麦从近期涨势中回落，但全球供应困境限制了损失</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/grains-wheat-retreats-from-recent-rally-but-global-supply-woes-limit-losses/articleshow/110287885.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110287885.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于美国冬季作物评级下降和俄罗斯霜冻损害，芝加哥小麦期货在上涨近 6% 后回落。大豆和玉米价格也下跌，而美国农业部报告了作物状况。澳大利亚农作物面临干燥天气的威胁，乌克兰北部和东部的严重霜冻也可能减少谷物和油籽收成。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 03:27:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/grains-wheat-retreats-from-recent-rally-but-global-supply-woes-limit-losses/articleshow/110287885.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>